  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Fish Shop Simulator</i> you manage your own aquatic store in a cozy New York neighborhood. Build your dream aquarium business by carefully selecting fish, aquariums, and decorations to create beautiful underwater environments for your customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run your own aquarium shop</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Serve a variety of customers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298720/extras/90db445e6c0f3cf8851fcc1befd8e36d.poster.avif?t=1743523845\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298720/extras/90db445e6c0f3cf8851fcc1befd8e36d.webm?t=1743523845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298720/extras/90db445e6c0f3cf8851fcc1befd8e36d.mp4?t=1743523845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design and sell custom aquariums</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298720/extras/1713678edfad07765d274b1337d0a942.poster.avif?t=1743523845\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298720/extras/1713678edfad07765d274b1337d0a942.webm?t=1743523845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298720/extras/1713678edfad07765d274b1337d0a942.mp4?t=1743523845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new items, aquariums, and rare fish as you grow your shop and attract more customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298720/extras/ea4fcfb5fff8e658d10d953f730f641c.poster.avif?t=1743523845\" width=576 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298720/extras/ea4fcfb5fff8e658d10d953f730f641c.webm?t=1743523845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298720/extras/ea4fcfb5fff8e658d10d953f730f641c.mp4?t=1743523845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep track of supplies, and shop decorations to maintain a thriving business.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298720/extras/247af36316402b244becacdc955d5197.poster.avif?t=1743523845\" width=576 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298720/extras/247af36316402b244becacdc955d5197.webm?t=1743523845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298720/extras/247af36316402b244becacdc955d5197.mp4?t=1743523845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a blend of casual management and creative design as you shape your store into an underwater paradise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
